  <summary date="2017-01-13T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Military Residency Choice Act

This bill amends the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act to permit the spouse of a servicemember to elect to use the same residence as the servicemember for purposes of taxation and voting, regardless of the date on which the marriage of the spouse and the servicemember occurred.</summary>
